names: Edge of the World Keshta via Manjour Trail
description:
Discover the magic of Saudi Arabiaโs breathtaking landscapes on an unforgettable adventure along the Manjour Trail leading to the iconic Edge of the World, a must-see destination for Riyadh travelers. This unique route offers a blend of natural beauty and ancient history, making it one of the top activities in Riyadh for nature lovers and adventure seekers alike.
Begin your journey with a scenic drive in a comfortable Sedan through the rugged desert terrain. Travel past rocky escarpments, serene plateaus, and ancient fossil-lined paths as you explore the untouched wilderness of the Manjour Trailโa hidden gem!
Arrive at the other side of the majestic Edge of the World, where a guided hike takes you to the summit of the dramatic Tuwaiq Mountains, offering awe-inspiring panoramic views of the vast Arabian desert. These endless vistas make for stunning photo opportunities and moments of serene solitude, perfect for capturing unforgettable memories.
